.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: More advice</span><hr size=1> Follow your heart, your head has been programmed to take irrelevant info into account....<br><br><br>and, your heart leads a much more exciting life than your head does. <p></p><span class=m><i></i></span><hr size=1>   &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=http://pub110.ezboard.com/favvisionefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=339.topic&index=1><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/reply.gif border=0 width=20 height=20 alt="reply to this message" align=absmiddle></a>   <br><br></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#949494><td colspan=2><table cellpadding=8 cellspacing=0 width=100%><tr><td nowrap width=20% valign=top><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub49.ezboard.com/ucamrael.showPublicProfile?language=EN>camrael</A> </span><br><br> <span class=usertitle>Nukerator</span><br>  Posts: <b>638</b><br></td><td valign=top align=left class=m width=80%><span class=m><font color=#000000>Posted: 10/8/01 11:07:01 am</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><br><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_geek.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: More advice</span><hr size=1> Aye, your brain is concerned with mundane things like, how much do I need to digest this for, or let's put some more blood in my arm, its like an accountant/projectmanager in one, and who would listen to either of those functionaries for love.<br><br> <p></p><span class=m><i></i></span><hr size=1>   &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=http://pub110.ezboard.com/favvisionefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=339.topic&index=2><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/reply.gif border=0 width=20 height=20 alt="reply to this message" align=absmiddle></a>   <br><br></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#9D9D9D><td colspan=2><table cellpadding=8 cellspacing=0 width=100%><tr><td nowrap width=20% valign=top><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub49.ezboard.com/ugebichan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>GebiChan</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_star.gif" BORDER=0> </span><br><BR><img src=http://www.noows.com/images/avatars/scoobydoo.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60><br> <span class=usertitle>Elf'Lover</span><br>  Posts: <b>579</b><br></td><td valign=top align=left class=m width=80%><span class=m><font color=#000000>Posted: 10/8/01 11:32:59 am</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><br><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_geek.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: More advice</span><hr size=1> Depends on what will lead you to happier and better life. I mean if your head is telling you one thing say leading you to a easy way of life where the streets are paved with gold, but the path your heart wants is a lower step in life. Does Gold make you happy or will the lower step make you happy? One will be easier but will it be happier? Does easier = better? Not in all cases. Some of the riches people are lonely depressed and day dreaming about living in their past. Best decisions in life are those made when the heart and head agree. <br><br>Does the heart and head always come to an agreement nope, in most cases they never do. Thats why it is up to you, to know yourself and what in the long run makes you the happiest in life. Only you alone can choise the best path.<br><br><br>                      Me, Myself,  And I<br><br>Sometimes in life we sit and wait for things to come our way. Sometimes we push to get that what we want. Sometimes we follow, somtimes we lead. Sometimes we let our heart guide us over bumps that could have been voided. Sometimes we play it smart and watch for little unexpected things in life. But out of all we do as a human race the best things are done on a leap of faith. Not in a god, or in a love, but in one person, ME, MYSELF, and I.<br><br>Not one person can choose to void downs in life, but one person can make them better. Not one person can hold you back. If the faith you have in yourself is strong, you will stride. Not one person can hold back tears why they make choices that will determine a way of life. One person can take a step, a jump, a leap, a fall and try. In the trying we may tear, hurt for a moment, or feel the sting of a million emotions. In one single step, you become the ME, MYSELF, and I.<br><br>Not a follower, not a leader, not a friend, not a sister, not a brother, just a single person. Who will live with all lives happiness, cause you believe in your choices and yourself. You now know the ME, MYSELF, and I.<br>-anon-<br><br> <p><img src="http://www.avvisione.com/members/Gabi.jpg" border="0"></a> </p><span class=m><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub49.ezboard.com/ugebichan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>GebiChan</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_star.gif" BORDER=0> at: 10/8/01 11:48:06 am<br></i></span><hr size=1>   &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=http://pub110.ezboard.com/favvisionefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=339.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/reply.gif border=0 width=20 height=20 alt="reply to this message" align=absmiddle></a>   <br><br></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#949494><td colspan=2><table cellpadding=8 cellspacing=0 width=100%><tr><td nowrap width=20% valign=top><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub49.ezboard.com/ulystrahawknorthernfury.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lystrahawk Northernfury</A> </span><br><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  ezSupporter<br> Posts: <b>21</b><br></td><td valign=top align=left class=m width=80%><span class=m><font color=#000000>Posted: 10/8/01 11:34:09 pm</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><br><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_yingyang.gif" align=absmiddle>